{"id": "1514993040136212602", "channel_id": "1514993040136212602", "type": 0, "author_id": "474412169249947669", "author_name": "komugi0506", "author_bot": false, "content": "Currently, Dtide rewards stop at 400 points, we do 425 mainly because the love for the game and want to push ourself to test the limit. Since 425 is by far one of the hardest achievements in the game, I think it would be nice to have some form of recognition for players who reach it.\n\nI understand why there are currently no rewards at 425 points. If valuable materials, currency, or progression resources were locked behind it, many players could feel pressured or fomo. So I think a purely cosmetic reward would be suitable.\n\nFor example, players who achieve 425 points could receive a 1 time avatar and a limit avatar frame that lasts just for 2-4 weeks (1-2 dtide seasons). When it expires, we would need to reach 425 points again to keep it.\n\nI think Dtide 425 is an accomplishment worthy of recognition and this kind of reward would help show appreciation for players who invest the time and effort to conquer the hardest challenge in the game without creating power gaps since the reward provides no gameplay advantage. The frame just has limited time also not compete with the permanent reward from bought content. \n\nI hope you can considering this suggestion. \nThank you very much.", "timestamp": "2026-06-12T14:01:27.978000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1514993040136212602", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Suggestion: Add a cosmetic reward for 425 points in D-Tide", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"], "is_thread_starter": true}
