{"id": "1514900963994112060", "channel_id": "1514900963994112060", "type": 0, "author_id": "422766128826417152", "author_name": "blackdonut5182", "author_bot": false, "content": "Could you please adjust the position of the icon for using the silver key and the icon for setting the playback speed a little?\n\nIt is inconvenient because the speed setting icon gets pressed every time I try to use the silver key.\n\nIt's not urgent, but this problem occurs too often.\nI'm not the only one, right?\n\n能否稍微調整一下銀鍵圖示和播放速度調節圖示的位置？\n\n每次想用銀鍵的時候，都會誤觸到速度調節圖標，很不方便。\n\n雖然不緊急，但這個問題出現的頻率太高了。\n\n應該不只我一個人遇到這個問題吧？", "timestamp": "2026-06-12T07:55:35.315000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-12T07:59:01.756000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [{"id": "1514901829929013278", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 15518, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1514900963994112060/1514901829929013278/image.png?ex=6a2db685&is=6a2c6505&hm=ce91ef9791675e12d88ade4f1393b674ed4226e0de513633b06ec06fedd33509&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1514900963994112060", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Suggestion for adjusting icon position", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"], "is_thread_starter": true}
